使用ArmorItems:[{}{}{}{}]从下往上，即鞋子到头盔这样数。

比如说：
/summon ArmorStand ~ ~ ~ {NoGravity:1b,Invulnerable:1b,ShowArms:1b,ArmorItems:[0:{id:"minecraft:leather_boots",Count:1b,tag:{display:{color:10168}},Damage:0s},1:{id:"minecraft:leather_leggings",Count:1b,tag:{display:{color:1321354}},Damage:0s},2:{id:"minecraft:leather_chestplate",Count:1b,tag:{display:{color:9127240}},Damage:0s},3:{id:"minecraft:leather_helmet",Count:1b,tag:{display:{color:138864}},Damage:0s}],NoBasePlate:1b}
